        "id": 1079748
      },
      "writtenOn": "2016-03-23T22:23:44Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Option 1: -2. Sounds horrible\n\nWhy does the result callback block? Because the user is being told that there was an error? Then we shouldn\u0027t be starting another install.\n\nI\u0027d say, immediately fail another attempt to start if we\u0027re still inFlight.\n\nAnd what assertion failure? I\u0027d like to understand the issue a bit better here.",
      "parentUuid": "7c21d2e1_0a3f97bb",
      "range": {
        "startLine": 190,
        "startChar": 8,
